.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noah-kahan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noah-kahan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noah-kahan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">诺亚·卡汉（Noah Kahan）</a>分享了有关他即将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/british-summer-time-bst-festival">伦敦BST海德公园（BST Hyde Park）</a>上的老虎机的更多细节，其中包括与他一起支持的艺术家。在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/noah-kahan-in-london-setlist-photos-3587843">伦敦的Noah Kahan：崛起的民间流行超级巨星毕业生</a></strong></li></ul><p>即将举行的演出将使这位民间流行歌手迄今为止扮演他最大的英国标题节目，并定于7月4日星期五在首都举行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noah-kahan-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3809226">演出的消息最初是在11月分享的</a>，还确认他将与歌手兼作曲家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">格雷西·艾布拉姆斯（Gracie Abrams）</a>一起加入。</p><p>现在，该节目宣布了更多名字，包括10次赢得格莱美奖的词曲作者和制片人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">Finneas</a> 。除了与他的姐姐比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）在她最大的发行版上紧密合作外，这位艺术家还在2019年分享了他的独奏首张EP“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/finneas-blood-harmony-review-2553557">血液和谐</a>”。即将到来的老虎机将出现，以庆祝<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finneas-announces-second-album-for-cryin-out-loud-with-hopeful-title-track-3782171">他最近共享的大二专辑“ For Cryin for Cryin&#39;Out Loud！”。</a></p><p>美国歌手兼作曲家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gigi-perez">吉吉·佩雷斯（Gigi Perez）</a>也加入了该法案。该插槽是按照她强大的首张EP“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gigi-perez-new-ep-how-to-catch-a-falling-knife-radar-3436543">如何捕捉摔落的刀</a>”和粉丝喜欢的曲目之类的，例如“当她微笑时”，“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/gigi-perez-interview-radar-breakout-sailor-song-3818056">Sailor Song</a> ”和“ Hill for You”。</p><p>德比郡的词曲作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paris-paloma">巴黎·帕利马（Paris Paloma）</a>也是如此，他是阵容的另一个新成员，并首先以病毒突破单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/paris-paloma-artist-labour-song-interview-tiktok-radar-3449655">劳动</a>”而闻名。从那以后，她继续筹集了一个忠实的粉丝群，并分享了她去年的首张专辑《 Cacophony》。 </p><figure id="attachment_3850172" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3850172" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3850172" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bst-kahan@2000.jpg" alt="Noah Kahan BST海德公园海报" width="2000" height="2820" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bst-kahan@2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bst-kahan@2000-400x564.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bst-kahan@2000-800x1128.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bst-kahan@2000-696x981.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bst-kahan@2000-1392x1963.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bst-kahan@2000-1068x1506.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3850172" class="wp-caption-text"> Noah Kahan BST海德公园海报。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>与Hyde Park一起加入Kahan的其他新名称包括澳大利亚出生的歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hazlett">Hazlett</a> ，独立流行歌手Jo Hill，德国出生的歌曲作者Sebastian Sebastian Schub，总部位于纳什维尔的悉尼罗斯，民间艺术家Kevin Atwater和23岁的Indie-Folk-Folk Lyrilk Lily Fitts。</p><p>除了Kahan，BST Hyde Park 2025宣布的其他头条新闻还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neil-young">Neil Young</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-second-show-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2025-buy-tickets-3839275">Sabrina Carpenter</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-her-biggest-ever-uk-show-at-bst-hyde-park-2025-3811479">Olivia Rodrigo</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zach-bryan-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3806223">Zach Bryan</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bst-hyde-park-2025-stevie-wonder-announced-as-final-headliner-3846750">Stevie Wonder</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeff-lynnes-elo-bst-hyde-park-2025-support-acts-announced-3834013">Jeff Lynne的Elo</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Famerican-express-presents-bst-hyde-park-tickets%2Fartist%2F1842565" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问这里</a>购买门票。</p><p> BST Hyde Park 2024带有头条新闻<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-stevie-nicks-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-3765318">Stevie Nicks</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-at-bst-hyde-park-2024-london-stage-times-3774511">Kylie Minogue</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/special-guests-announced-for-stray-kids-london-bst-hyde-park-show-3763729">Stray Kids</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-sza-at-bst-hyde-park-2024-3760887">Sza</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/more-support-acts-added-to-kings-of-leons-london-bst-hyde-park-2024-show-3762832">Leon的Kings</a> ，Leon， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3598527">Morgan Wallen</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hans-zimmer-seal-and-more-announced-as-special-guests-for-andrea-bocelli-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3763248">Andrea Bocelli</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3553493">Robbie Williams</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-shania-twain-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3764110">Shania Twain</a> 。</p><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/noah-kahan-in-london-setlist-photos-3587843"><em>NME</em></a>在情人节（2月14日）在情人节（2月14日）举行的卡汉（Kahan）在Wembley的OVO竞技场演出。</p><p>它写道：“又使民间流行音乐再次凉爽 - 也许是一个公平的嘲笑，因为&#39;Stomp clap hey&#39;音乐 - 不可否认，戴上火炬的Troubadour是可以打出巨大的阶段的。” “八月在伦敦的O2的标题表演，一个比这更大的场地，看起来像是在公园散步。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noah-kahan-bst-hyde-park-2025-support-acts-announced-finnea